Direct Known Subclasses:
BackgroundPanel, DifficultyPanel, EscapeMenuPanel, HighscorePanel, InGamePanel, InstructionsBg, InstructionsPanel, MainMenuPanel, NewGamePanel
public class GraphicalPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel

The class GraphicalPanel represents the basic panel used by the other classes in the Panels package. It contains one class which creates a new grid to be used by the other classes of this package.

1.0
